cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques for weed detection and classification in agricultural fields using multispectral images collected by a micro aerial vehicle (MAV). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves robotics and automation in agriculture, which falls under the sub-category cs.RO (Robotics). The use of machine learning algorithms for classification and prediction makes it relevant to sub-categories cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also involves the use of image processing techniques and feature extraction, which falls under the sub-category cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
